            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Children's parks are not under proper maintenance, and the bathrooms are also not maintained properly, kids are always complaining that there are a lot of bad smells coming out, I have also personally visited and observed the same thing, I have complained about this to management many times but there is no action taken till date,\n\nThe car parking area is too bad during the rainy season, it will be full of sludge and kids are not even able to get down from the car or bike, I don't know what the management guys are doing.",
