          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "2",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Velammal Vidhyashram in Mambakkam is not a great place to learn. The teachers are okay but the management are not doing a good job. They changed the principal)5 times in one year! This means there is no stability and the school is not being run well. This can make it hard for students to learn and have a good school experience. It's better to look into other schools in the area that are more stable and better for students. Overall, it was a poor experience.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
