            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Excellent school with very good infrastructure and knowledge sharing sessions. All events are being planned well with many interactive sessions. Thanks a lot for giving us comfort and feeling proud to say our daughter is a Velammal student. Special thanks to Geetha Mam of JKG A for all opportunities and care.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
