            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I can see a lots of positive reviews past one week about this school from kg students parents. Are they asking parents to put such reciews LOL. 🤔.  Few kids from our community study here in higher grades say they change teachers frequently and not a good place to put the kids. For the high amount charged in the name of cbse holistic education to be provided. Look before you leap",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
