          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-21",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter has attended two years in Velammal Vidhyashram, Mambakkam.\nWe are happy with the quality of education provided in Velammal Vidhyashram and it is one of best schools in Chennai.\nTeachers posses excellent skills and very helpful. They encourage students develop confidence, optimism and self respect.\nProject based learnings helped my daughter improve her problem solving abilities and identify individual strengths.\nAcademic program in Velammal Vidhyashram is well organized and we thank the teachers for being very supportive!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Velammal Vidhyashram - Mambakkam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Gayathri Selvan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-21",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son is studying Prekg in here .Personally I would recommend the school for their effective and extensive learning methods which are interesting for kids to learn and grow along . Their project based learning mechanism helped my son to show interest in gardening . And the staff here along with helpers also show patience and address the concerns of these kids with ease and move along wth kid very comfortably. I am really convinced and pleased by their academics and their method to inculcate a schedule even from prekg itself. Thank you",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
